machine_end_gcode:
G91
; Don't retract extra filament because we end up retracting on a tool change
; and we don't want to run the risk of going too far with molten filament.
; G1 E-3 F1800           ; Retract some extra filament
G1 Z+10                ; Move the nozzle up
G90

G1 Y370 F24000
T-1                    ; park the extruder

M400                   ; wait for all planned moves to finish!

M106 S0 P0             ; Turn off cooling fans
M106 S0 P2             ; Turn off cooling fans
M568 P0 R0 S0          ; Turn off extruders
M568 P1 R0 S0          ; Turn off extruders
M140 S0                ; Turn off bed
M84                    ; Disable motors
